timelineItems.name: Jacob
timelineItems.text: How many times will the Timbers get Rimando'd tonight? #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Tyler Gray
timelineItems.text: 7 points separate these sides, If RSL can pull off a win, that shrinks to just 4. They're still very much in the playoff race. #RSLvPOR

timelineItems.name: Jamie Goldberg
timelineItems.text: 8' - RSL's Silva puts a shot from the top of the box way over the net #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Chris Rifer
timelineItems.text: Those early long balls have really opened this up early. I'm ambivalent about that. #rctid

timelineItems.name: Tyler Gray
timelineItems.text: Garcia has looked great so far. I wouldn't be surprised if gets either a goal or an assist tonight. #RSLvPOR

timelineItems.desc: Demar Phillips (Real Salt Lake) is shown the yellow card for a bad foul.
timelineItems.title: YELLOW CARD: Demar Phillips pulls down Darlington Nagbe after a dazzling run

timelineItems.name: Tyler Gray
timelineItems.text: RSL have to start centering that ball to Javi at the top of the box. He's been open a number of times already. #RSLvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers

timelineItems.name: Jeremy Horton
timelineItems.text: 12' Philips picks up a yellow for a professional foul. Good idea - Nagbe was off to the races. #RSL

timelineItems.text: Looks like Fischer had that yellow out before the whistle. Philips stops a remarkable break by Nagbe. #RSLvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 12' - Nagbe steals ball from Beckerman and shoots off. Phillips grabs him and earns a yellow for it. #RCTID

timelineItems.text: THIS GUY THO💪🏼💪🏼💪🏼 #RSLvPOR http://t.co/UAWdeElRmG

timelineItems.name: Tyler Gray
timelineItems.text: Jaime almost side volleys a beautiful shot into the net but it sails just over the bar. RSL is heating up. #RSLvPOR

timelineItems.name: Nathan Miller

timelineItems.name: Rob Robinette
timelineItems.text: Have I mentioned lately how much I like Diego Chara? #RCTID
